gantt
    title Car Purchase Timing Diagram (Typical Flow)
    dateFormat  HH:mm
    axisFormat  %H:%M

    section Car (ID: 101)
    Available          :active, c1, 00:00, 2h
    Reserved (Pending) :c2, after c1, 8h
    Sold               :crit, c3, after c2, 4h

    section Contract (ID: 501)
    Customer Browsing  :b1, 00:00, 2h
    Request Created    :milestone, 02:00, 0s
    Pending Approval   :p1, 02:00, 8h
    Admin Approval     :milestone, 10:00, 0s
    Completed          :p2, 10:00, 4h

    section User Session
    Guest              :s1, 00:00, 1h
    Login (johndoe)    :s2, 01:00, 11h
    Logout             :s3, 12:00, 2h
